title: ENCHANTED HOLLOWS
description: ONE OF THE BEST NEW HALLOWEEN EVENTS IN DENVER.  EXPERIENCE ENCHANTED HOLLOWS NIGHT WALK. If you’re tired of Denver haunted houses, it’s time to travel an eerie trail where the darkness has almost all but taken hold, creatures and spirits infamous in stories and lore, rise to life in the new Enchanted Hollows night walk experience. If you’re looking for new things to do for teens and adults at Halloween, this is one of the eeriest and most unique Denver experiences at it’s only at Denver Zoo.
